Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你說你扎進電視裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和里中倒是都看到了奇怪的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子你看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我之前和你說的那個「午夜電視」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅館很忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那麼加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雖然這肯定是夢之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為電視太小了所以沒能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是挺有真實感的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要是用大電視來試試看又會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要用JUNES的大型電視來試試看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  怎麼真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不妥嗎  我家正好也想換電視了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你開個後門賣便宜點？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是這家店店長的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是從城裡轉到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是半年前轉來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說JUNES建成之後是方便了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是商業街就變冷清了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就直接當著我的面說這種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不喜歡在背後說別人的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你有沒有在這附近發現什麼可疑人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個人和小西學姐很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上也有人傳言說小西學姐就是第一發現者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她今天才請假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有回覆我的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎  扎進去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是施展的什麼障眼法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能進到更裡面一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡…裡面是指什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  因為太過吃驚我快憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼快憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不行了  出來了  要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有客人在  你要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  來了  來了  出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先找個地方躲起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拉我啊  喂  要出…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在電視裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在騙人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你別若無其事地說出這麼不得了的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這份疼痛證明了我們身處現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股好像裂成兩瓣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是兩瓣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我們究竟是從哪裡進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到入口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有霧  所以看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啊  我要回去  我想立刻就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說要回去  但該怎麼回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  剛才那個怪東西好像沒跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張海報…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的膀胱已經快要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原來是這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你要在這裡解決嗎  饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你快阻止他啊  鳴上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被別人看著我根本尿不出來啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  真是的  要是得了膀胱炎那都是你們兩個害的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管你啊  我才不想看你那東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要問你們是誰呢熊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說話了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊就是熊熊的說  我一直都住在這裡熊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在說些什麼啊  真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要發出這麼大的聲音啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你們快點回那邊去吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上這個  快點回去吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow要  Shadow要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你為什麼要戴眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  出現了熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里中～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已  已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳…動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即為汝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝即為…吾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.56,0:24:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們停下來了  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.22,0:24:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝  睜開雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻啟程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.50,0:24:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PE…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.99,0:24:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.38,0:25:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SO…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.74,0:25:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NA！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.36,0:25:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴上？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.64,0:25:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.61,0:26:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊邪那岐！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.66,0:26:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.54,0:26:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.33,0:26:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的力量
